On Windows
Install:
VirtualBox
Ubuntu 22.04 ISO from Ubuntu Official Website
Then:
Create Ubuntu VM inside VirtualBox
Start Ubuntu
STEP 1 — Open Ubuntu VM

Start Ubuntu 22.04 in VirtualBox.

STEP 2 — Open Terminal
STEP 3 — Create Project Folder
mkdir dashboard

Go inside folder:

cd dashboard
STEP 4 — Create HTML File
gedit index.html

This opens text editor.

Paste this complete code:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>Admin Dashboard</title>

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body{
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    .sidebar{
      height:100vh;
      background:#212529;
      color:white;
      padding-top:20px;
    }

    .sidebar a{
      color:white;
      text-decoration:none;
      display:block;
      padding:10px;
    }

    .sidebar a:hover{
      background:#495057;
    }

    .card{
      box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">

    <div class="col-md-2 sidebar">
      <h3 class="text-center">Dashboard</h3>

      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#">Students</a>
      <a href="#">Courses</a>
      <a href="#">Exams</a>
      <a href="#">Settings</a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-10 p-4">

      <h2>College Admin Dashboard</h2>

      <div class="row mt-4">

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-center p-3">
            <h5>Total Students</h5>
            <h2>1200</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-center p-3">
            <h5>Total Courses</h5>
            <h2>45</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-center p-3">
            <h5>Exams Conducted</h5>
            <h2>32</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="card text-center p-3">
            <h5>Faculty Members</h5>
            <h2>85</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>

Save file.

STEP 5 — Open Webpage

In terminal:

firefox index.html

OR double click the file.
